description: This data model is to help check adoption into the CIM.  It provides useful objects for making sure things are tagged appropriately and verify key fields for the different models are not missing.

constraints.search: All_Application_State.is_Ports=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR dest_port=0 OR transport="unknown")
All_Application_State.is_Processes=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR process="unknown")
All_Application_State.is_Services=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR service="unknown" OR start_mode="unknown")
(action="unknown" OR app="unknown" OR src="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR user="unknown")
ssl_hash="unknown" OR ssl_issuer="unknown" OR ssl_subject="unknown"

All_Changes.is_Endpoint_Changes=1 AND (action="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR object="unknown" OR object_category="unknown" OR object_path="unknown" OR status="unknown" OR user="unknown")

All_Changes.is_Endpoint_Changes=1 AND (object_category=file OR object_category=directory) AND (action="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR object="unknown" OR object_category="unknown" OR object_path="unknown" OR status="unknown" OR user="unknown" OR file_access_time=0 OR file_create_time=0 OR file_hash="unknown" OR file_modify_time=0 OR file_name="unknown" OR file_path="unknown" OR file_acl="unknown" OR file_size="unknown")
All_Changes.is_Network_Changes=1 AND (action="unknown" OR command="unknown" OR dvc="unknown" OR user="unknown")
All_Changes.is_Network_Changes=1 AND (action="unknown" OR change_type="unknown") AND (reboot* OR restart*) sourcetype!=stash
All_Inventory.is_CPU=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT (cpu_cores=* OR cpu_count=* OR cpu_mhz=*))
All_Inventory.is_Memory=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT (mem=*))
All_Inventory.is_Network=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT (interface=* OR ip=* OR mac=* OR name=* OR dns=*))
All_Inventory.is_Storage=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT (mount=* OR storage=*))
All_Inventory.is_OS=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT (os=* OR version=*))
(action="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR src="unknown" OR src_user="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")
(dvc="unknown" OR ids_type="unknown" OR category="unknown" OR signature="unknown" OR severity="unknown" OR src="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR user="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")
(action="unknown" OR category="unknown" OR signature="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR dest_nt_domain="unknown" OR user="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")
dest="unknown" OR dest_nt_domain="unknown" OR product="unknown" OR (NOT (product_version=* OR signature_version=*)) OR vendor="unknown"
src="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR answer="unknown" OR query="unknown" OR message_type="unknown" OR reply_code="unknown"
(dest_ip="unknown")
(action="unknown" OR dvc="unknown" OR rule="unknown" OR transport="unknown" OR src="unknown" OR src_port=0 OR dest="unknown" OR dest_port=0 OR vendor_product="unknown")
All_Performance.is_CPU=1 AND ((dest="unknown" OR NOT (cpu_load_mhz=* OR cpu_load_percent=* OR cpu_time=* OR cpu_user_percent=*)))
All_Performance.is_Facilities=1 AND ((dest="unknown" OR NOT (temperature=* OR power=* OR fan_speed=*)))
All_Performance.is_Memory=1 AND ((dest="unknown" OR NOT (mem=* OR mem_committed=* OR mem_free=* OR mem_used=*)))
All_Performance.is_Storage=1 AND ((dest="unknown" OR NOT (mount=* OR storage=* OR storage_free=* OR storage_used=* OR storage_free_percent=* OR storage_used_percent=*)))
All_Performance.is_Network=1 AND ((dest="unknown" OR NOT (thruput=* OR thruput_max=*)))
All_Performance.is_OS=1 AND (tag=time tag=synchronize (dest="unknown" OR action="unknown"))
All_Performance.is_OS=1 AND (tag=uptime (dest="unknown" OR uptime="unknown"))
dest="unknown" OR ticket_id="unknown"
All_Ticket_Management.is_Incident=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR incident="unknown")
All_Ticket_Management.is_Problem=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR problem="unknown")
All_Ticket_Management.is_Change=1 AND (dest="unknown" OR NOT change="unknown")
(dest="unknown" OR signature="unknown" OR signature_id="unknown" OR status="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")
(dvc="unknown" OR category="unknown" OR signature="unknown" OR severity="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")

(action="unknown" OR dest="unknown" OR http_content_type="unknown" OR http_method="unknown" OR http_referrer="unknown" OR http_user_agent="unknown" OR src="unknown" OR status="unknown" OR url="unknown" OR user="unknown" OR vendor_product="unknown")
(listen OR listening OR open) (port OR ports) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=listening tag=port)
(process) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=process tag=report)
(running OR stopped OR runlevel* OR service) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=service tag=report)
(login OR "log in" OR authenticated) sourcetype!=stash NOT tag=authentication
(change OR changed OR modify OR modified OR restart* OR reboot*) sourcetype!=stash NOT tag=change
(postfix OR sendmail OR rcpts OR nrcpts OR recipients OR msgid OR message-id) sourcetype!=stash NOT tag=email
(sourcetype=*idp* OR sourcetype=*ids* OR intrusion OR hip) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=ids tag=attack)
(virus OR malware OR infection OR infected) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=malware tag=attack)
(BIND) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=network tag=resolution)
(*dhcp* OR *vpn) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=network tag=session)
(accept OR drop) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=network tag=communicate)
(cpu OR cputime OR mhz OR ghz) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=performance tag=cpu)
(power OR temperature) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=performance tag=facilities)
(mem OR memory) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=performance tag=memory)
(mount OR disk OR df) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=performance tag=storage)
(net OR network) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=performance tag=network)
sourcetype!=stash (((uptime OR systemuptime) NOT (tag=performance tag=os tag=uptime)) OR (time sync* NOT (tag=performance tag=os tag=time tag=synchronize)))
(update OR updates OR installed OR "restart required" OR available OR patch) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=update tag=status)
(sourcetype=*vuln* OR "vulnerability detected" OR CVE) sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=vulnerability tag=report)
http sourcetype!=stash NOT (tag=web)
